OL,3,CShop owners in Jersey lament low
OL,4,CChristmas shopping sales
OL,6,FThe owner of the oldest shop in Jersey
OL,7,Fsays it's been their worst-ever
OL,8,FChristmas trading period - down 50% on
OL,9,Flast year.
OL,11,FThe Red Triangle in St Helier's
OL,12,FCentral Market says they've seen a
OL,13,Fsignificant drop in footfall.
OL,15,FShop owner Sheila Baudains: "This is
OL,16,Fthe worst Christmas trade I've had in
OL,17,Fthe 10 years I've been here.
OL,19,F"We are struggling. If you don't use
OL,20,Fus you'll lose us. It would be
OL,21,Fhorrible to see us go."
