OL,3,CShop owners in Jersey lament low
OL,4,CChristmas shopping sales
OL,6,FJohn Testori, who runs Bambola, shares
OL,7,FSheila's fears. He explains: "The
OL,8,Ffirst half of the month was really
OL,9,Fstrong and then the storm came along
OL,10,Fand I think people have just left town
OL,11,Falone since then.
OL,13,F"Access is a huge issue trying to park
OL,14,Fis a nightmare, lack of parking, no
OL,15,Faccess down Broad Street, no one walks
OL,16,Fdown Broad Street and you can't drive
OL,17,Fdown it, it's got nothing left of the
OL,18,Fstreet."
