OL,3,CShop owners in Jersey lament low
OL,4,CChristmas shopping sales
OL,6,FChannel Island shoppers say there are
OL,7,Fa range of reasons they are swerving
OL,8,Fthe high street in favour of online
OL,9,Fshopping.
OL,11,FOne shopper said: "Most of (my
OL,12,Fshopping) is being done online at the
OL,13,Fmoment.
OL,15,F"The prices are just not that
OL,16,Fcompelling locally I get most of it on
OL,17,FAmazon."
OL,19,FAnother added: "It's just so much
OL,20,Feasier online you can get it at the
OL,21,Fclick of a button at any time of day."
