OL,3,CShop owners in Jersey lament low
OL,4,CChristmas shopping sales
OL,6,FOthers said the recent cost of living
OL,7,Fpressures meant they were spending
OL,8,Fless this year.
OL,10,FOne islander said: "It's just a bit
OL,11,Ftight these days isn't it for
OL,12,Feveryone, so we are probably spending
OL,13,Fless on Christmas generally rather
OL,14,Fthan not spending on the high street."
OL,16,FWith an increasing number of shops
OL,17,Flying empty, Jersey's government says
OL,18,Fit will roll out a new retail strategy
OL,19,Fwithin the next few weeks to help
OL,20,Fbusinesses change as customers adapt.
