OL,3,CShop owners in Jersey lament low
OL,4,CChristmas shopping sales
OL,6,FDeputy Kirsten Morel, Economic
OL,7,FDevelopment Minister, says: "It's
OL,8,Fimportant that Jersey's retailers
OL,9,Fadapt and that they do also themselves
OL,10,Fengage in online sales.
OL,12,F"We will be issuing very shortly
OL,13,Fwithin the next week or so our retail
OL,14,Fstrategy which is designed to enable
OL,15,Fthe town centre to grow and thrive in
OL,16,FJersey."
